column5: Lots of changes this year, rebuilt my evinrude first marine 2 stroke for me, got married and opened a business, somewhere in all of that even got out fishing just not as much as i liked but who gets out as much as they want, heres a couple pics from the year.  sturgeon lake
some nice bass there and good luck with the new business
Looks like a decent season to me. Its hard to look at all your summer pics at this time of year. only 6 months till bass opener !
Lots of positive changes for you ecmilley  Congrats   Good luck with your new business Nice mix bag of fishes too Leechman
Great stuff!  Wish you all the best with your new business.  Congrats on getting married  and screw you for making me miss summer!
